# docs/waves/ — Wave plans + summaries

One folder per wave. Opens with `PLAN.md`, closes with `SUMMARY.md`. See `docs/GNGM/docs/06-WAVE-PROTOCOL.md` for lifecycle.

## Wave status

_(populate as waves open)_

**Legend:** ⚫ not started · 🟡 open · 🟢 executing · 🔵 in review · 🔴 blocked · ✅ closed

## Conventions

- Create folder on wave open: `docs/waves/wave-N-<shortname>/`
- `PLAN.md` — pre-execute plan (see 06-WAVE-PROTOCOL.md stage 1)
- `SUMMARY.md` — post-close summary (see 06-WAVE-PROTOCOL.md stage 7)
- `DEVIATION.md` — if mid-wave scope/design changes materially
- `assets/` — wave-specific artifacts (diagrams, screenshots, research exports)

